<section id="all-features" class="all-features">
  <div class="grid grid-3">
    <h3>All the features!</h3>
    <h2>Go ahead, get out your checklist of must-haves &amp; deal-breakers</h2>

    <div class="column first">
      <img src="/img/design_align/icons/icon-security-and-privacy.svg" alt="" />
      <h4>Security &amp; privacy</h4>
      <p>HipChat's secure conversations are transferred in 256-bit SSL encryption &ndash; the same security protocol as online banks.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="column">
      <img src="/img/design_align/icons/icon-secure-guest-access.svg" alt="" />
      <h4>Secure guest access</h4>
      <p>Bring clients, vendors, and other third-parties into a HipChat room. They'll only see what you want them to see. You have complete control.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="column last">
      <img src="/img/design_align/icons/icon-easy-screen-sharing.svg" alt="" />
      <h4>Easy screen sharing</h4>
      <p>For when you need to show, not tell. Share your desktop with your colleagues on any device to collaborate in real time.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="column first">
      <img src="/img/design_align/icons/icon-drag-and-drop-file-sharing.svg" alt="" />
      <h4>Drag and drop file sharing</h4>
      <p>Grab files from your desktop, DropBox, email or anywhere. HipChat shows a preview of the file to everyone in the room.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="column">
      <img src="/img/design_align/icons/icon-unlimited-chat-rooms.svg" alt="" />
      <h4>Unlimited chat rooms</h4>
      <p>Create rooms for projects, teams, clients, or the lunchtime basketball league. When you're finished with a chat room just archive it.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="column last">
      <img src="/img/design_align/icons/icon-fully-customizable.svg" alt="" />
      <h4>Fully customizable</h4>
      <p>Customize how HipChat alerts you when you miss a message. Create a combination of in-app, email, SMS, and mobile push notifications.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="column first">
      <img src="/img/design_align/icons/icon-fully-searchable.svg" alt="" />
      <h4>Fully searchable</h4>
      <p>Every room is searchable by keyword, including text, links, files, and more. If it's discussed in HipChat, it's saved forever.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="column">
      <img src="/img/design_align/icons/icon-persistent.svg" alt="" />
      <h4>Persistent</h4>
      <p>HipChat synchronizes across desktop, mobile and web apps. Conversations are never lost when you switch devices.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="column last">
      <img src="/img/design_align/icons/icon-time-traveling.svg" alt="" />
      <h4>Time traveling</h4>
      <p>Just kidding. But having a fully searchable history is sort of like time travel...</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

